        "body": "The Apache SeaTunnel official website is not responsive on mobile devices. When accessed on smaller screen sizes, the layout does not adapt correctly, resulting in fixed-width content, horizontal scrolling, and reduced readability.\n\nThis affects the usability of the website for users browsing documentation and project information on mobile devices.\n\nSteps to Reproduce\n\n1. Open https://seatunnel.apache.org\n2. Access the site on a mobile device or simulate a mobile viewport using browser developer tools\n3. Observe layout issues such as non-responsive navigation and overflowing content\n\nExpected Behaviour\n\nThe website should adapt to different screen sizes, with responsive layouts and readable content on mobile and tablet devices.\n\nAdditional Information\n\nI have opened this issue to track the improvement and am currently working on making the website responsive while keeping the existing design consistent.\n\nThis issue relates to the SeaTunnel website repository, where issues are currently disabled.",
